did.abstract: Collection consists of color and black and white 35 mm slides of architecture, worldwide.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: The materials are open for research.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Architecture Slide Collection, Arts Library, Yale University

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Collection consists of color and black and white 35 mm slides of architecture, worldwide.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: Arranged chronologically by period style. Built structures further arranged by country, then by city or other location, and building type. Unbuilt structures arranged by architect or firm name.
